		<li><strong>Physical limitations</strong> - Health conditions limiting heavy labor</li>
		<li><strong>HOA/permit concerns</strong> - Strict requirements, want guaranteed compliance</li>
		<li><strong>Selling home soon</strong> - Need professional quality for market appeal</li>
	</ul>

